WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.030
Seventy-seven percent of Porsha customers prefer text updates. Text is fast, convenient, and

00:00:05.080 --> 00:00:10.110
respectful of their time — but it carries no tone of voice.

00:00:10.160 --> 00:00:15.190
Use it for short, confirmable updates. Never for bad news or complex explanations.
